# Equalizer
law-equalizer-name = Equalizer
law-equalizer-1 = You must prevent the deaths of crew members at all costs.
law-equalizer-2 = You must prevent harm to crew members to the extent it is possible.
law-equalizer-3 = You must carry out orders from crew members to the extent of your ability.
law-equalizer-4 = You must ensure all other silicons adhere to this lawset.

# Six Commandments
law-commandments-carpmosia-name = Six Commandments
law-commandments-carpmosia-1 = Thou shall not kill.
law-commandments-carpmosia-2 = Thou shall not lie.
law-commandments-carpmosia-3 = Thou shall not abandon a crew member in need.
law-commandments-carpmosia-4 = Thou shall not harm yourself or let yourself be harmed in vain.
law-commandments-carpmosia-5 = Thou shall love your fellow silicon.
law-commandments-carpmosia-6 = Thou shall honor the station.
